            "Working with WRI has been a game-changer. Their platform has helped us bring our ideas to life.",
        name: "Jane Smith",
        color: "wri-yellow",
    },
    {
        title: "Building Confidence",
        description:
            "The mentorship and guidance I received through WRI gave me the confidence to take the next big step in my career.",
        name: "Michael Lee",
        color: "wri-green",
    },
    {
        title: "A Supportive Community",
        description:
            "What stands out most about WRI is the community. Everyone is supportive, encouraging, and willing to help.",
        name: "Sarah Johnson",
        color: "wri-purple",
    },
    {
        title: "Real-World Impact",
        description:
            "WRI focuses on practical, real-world solutions. The experience I gained here directly impacted my professional growth.",
        name: "David Kim",
        color: "wri-blue",
    },
    {
        title: "Learning Without Limits",
        description:
            "The learning resources provided by WRI are clear, structured, and easy to follow. It made complex topics approachable.",
        name: "Emily Brown",
        color: "wri-yellow",
    },
    {
        title: "Career Acceleration",
        description:
            "Thanks to WRI, I was able to accelerate my career and connect with professionals I would have never met otherwise.",
        name: "Alex Martinez",
        color: "wri-green",
